            <abstract>
            <p>This introduction to the Pauline Epistles states why, to whom and where Paul composed his epistles, 
            what he taught in them and through whom he sent them. It is similar, but apparently not identical, to 
                <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3199Introd#PaulineEpistles"/>.</p>
